Package task

Class DeadLine

  • java.lang.Object
    • task.Task
      • task.DeadLine
  • public class DeadLine
extends Task
    The `DeadLine` class represents a deadline task in the BloopBot application. It extends the base `Task` class and inherits its properties and methods. A `DeadLine` task includes a description and a deadline represented by a "by" string. It can be marked as completed or not completed. This class provides methods to create and format `DeadLine` tasks.

    0.0.0
